{"tid":2499793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"193@ERROR超越姜濤成新人氣王 IG fans一星期暴增逾十萬","createTime":"2021-04-22T06:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:52:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6b40d0828dcaa89cdf8578f3d46aaf0933c38f","tid":2499793,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/R6UFAPGOHJBSNLQMJAETRHOTH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FR6UFAPGOHJBSNLQMJAETRHOTH4%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clncv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=00343e3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FR6UFAPGOHJBSNLQMJAETRHOTH4%2F&h=df66e4c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/R6UFAPGOHJBSNLQMJAETRHOTH4/</a><br />\n<br />\n193@ERROR超越姜濤成新人氣王 IG fans一星期暴增逾十萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0UB07upX7r7rjpeXuzdi1AGqkZo=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4B7ZSALGW5BWHGNAHBMWRBD2NY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0UB07upX7r7rjpeXuzdi1AGqkZo%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4B7ZSALGW5BWHGNAHBMWRBD2NY.jpg&h=e31a36b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n組合ERROR成員193（郭嘉駿）因被指「講真話」而獲網民封做「三哥」和「三爺」，在這個星期中，人氣不但撼低ERROR隊員，就連以偶像掛帥的MIRROR 12位成員，193的氣勢亦可謂過之而無不及。至於IG的followers，更是錄得驚人增長，在本月12日，其IG只有8.9萬followers，但當他發表寸大台霸氣言論後，followers激增約2萬，其後193的IG人數每日都有接近1萬增長，直迫人氣王姜濤，到昨日（21日）晚上10時半，193的IG followers終於和姜濤打成平手，同獲20萬fans追蹤，以走勢來看，相信短時間內有望超越姜濤的fans人數。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：自薦代言丨193@ERROR親證「洽商中」 反省隨口噏：唔知自己咁有影響力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自稱是ERROR的姜濤<br />\n<br />\n對於短短一星期追平姜濤，193昨晚回應《蘋果》說：「其實冇話追唔追姜濤嘅，大家啲followers都有啲分別，姜濤嘅followers都會follow我囉，咁希望我嘅followers都會follow埋姜濤，咁就我好，姜濤好；姜濤好，我又好；咁就ERROR好，MIRROR又好；MIRROR又好，ERROR又好。同埋我成日都自稱係ERROR嘅姜濤，希望姜B會自稱為MIRROR嘅193囉。」<br />\n<br />\n以騎呢、搞笑形象突圍而出的193，竟然在短短一星期內就能與姜濤「平起平坐」，成為MIRROR和ERROR中的「新人氣王」，全因其率直個性，其寸大台金句有「收視點得嗰幾百部電視機，我哋不嬲都唔介意」、「佢哋係畀老嘢睇嘛」，又寸J2節目係「冇記錯係咪40幾歲仲話後生仔傾偈嗰個」，之後他回應大台自組「千禧五虎」時，又再衝口而出話「而家仲用五虎呢啲字咁娘㗎咩？」回應抵死又啜核，深得網民愛戴，紛紛封他為「娛樂圈清泉」，而其IG的followers亦因此而受惠。<br />\n<br />\n截至今早（22日）11時，193的IG 有20.5萬followers，已超越姜濤的20.2萬followers，認真犀利！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_5TyXIJ9qMbX7fEqteu6EcOtW1Y=/510x328/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MMDEXMMVZDSXEPCFDT7WDSPUA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_5TyXIJ9qMbX7fEqteu6EcOtW1Y%3D%2F510x328%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MMDEXMMVZDSXEPCFDT7WDSPUA.JPG&h=ae94a6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日最新戰況，193的IG followers已超越姜濤。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/57-0J0pbG9SEnZhhEqm5sLejr7M=/510x202/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AC7I4SUXVFGWNBIAGXOV5O43ZQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F57-0J0pbG9SEnZhhEqm5sLejr7M%3D%2F510x202%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAC7I4SUXVFGWNBIAGXOV5O43ZQ.JPG&h=5643b56f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜濤暫時落後3000 followers。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZHAnkLz6nDJR_f9zLcUaqr0L9mI=/412x519/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MET3YMXUGFDPLAN4VXJ2VJDPAE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZHAnkLz6nDJR_f9zLcUaqr0L9mI%3D%2F412x519%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMET3YMXUGFDPLAN4VXJ2VJDPAE.JPG&h=3c57524e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n193最近人氣急升。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MkuXjkaNH7E18h8Yvb07vOgZgvM=/419x525/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WEFMUHDEXBAKPCPJQB3SV4QDNM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMkuXjkaNH7E18h8Yvb07vOgZgvM%3D%2F419x525%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWEFMUHDEXBAKPCPJQB3SV4QDNM.JPG&h=722dfbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜濤（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_g1RWyQClUFV4cVLnRtZRhLhoMg=/510x117/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3FL5IJM655DFJDLJS4D65Q7Q44.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_g1RWyQClUFV4cVLnRtZRhLhoMg%3D%2F510x117%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3FL5IJM655DFJDLJS4D65Q7Q44.JPG&h=67c959aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n193在短短一星期IG人數暴升逾一倍，今晚終於破20萬大關。（IG截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-ZOu-tEUuN0y38REibmmueuAcjw=/510x292/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7G5DPNSMFFGENNXGIJL2TS2K6Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-ZOu-tEUuN0y38REibmmueuAcjw%3D%2F510x292%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7G5DPNSMFFGENNXGIJL2TS2K6Y.JPG&h=aa1ba54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜濤IG fans人數在昨晚亦衝破20萬，和193叮噹馬頭。（IG截圖）<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n蘋果App大升級 更簡潔更就手！了解更多（立即下載體驗）<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n蘋果初心不變！26周年「撐蘋果Tee」預售：<br />\n<br />\n你的優惠訂購（海外訂購按此）"},{"pid":"c242869500999fde2ad04649c86f5e35879ca282","tid":2499793,"uid":268712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:36:42.000Z"